data.description: Want to own a piece of history but with modern conveniences? This home is for you! It has all the charm of the 1900 Victorian without all the hassle while still keeping old world charm. Check out the 3 full bathrooms with unique features such as the black and white Parisian style bathroom or the 20th century gorgeous hardwoods and trim work throughout. This home also has a 3 car detached garage which allows for all your favorite toys to be stored easily, relax in the back patio or on the lovely wrap around porch. If you are looking to come home to relax and enjoy yourself this home really has it all! Roof on main house and detached garage new in 2022! Ask about assumable VA loan!
